text.tspan: A Love That Is Always There
Experience of Christ â€” Love for Him
Lord, You are always in control,
Able to calm my troubled soul,
And would my fears be here at all
If I just turned to You and called?
Oh! Oh, Hallelujah! A love so real.
Oh! Oh, Hallelujah! A love so rare, the way You care,
A love that is always there.
Lord, keep me always by Your side;
Guard me from all that would divide,
And light a fire deep in me,
Oh! Oh, Hallelujah! A love so real.
Oh! Oh, Hallelujah! A love so rare, the way You care,
A love that is always there.
Taking more time to call Your name,
Praying that more of You Iâ€™d gain,
Watching all things just pass away,
I cannot waste a single day.
Oh! Oh, Hallelujah! The time is now.
Oh! Oh, Hallelujah! The days are few, the world is through,
Lord, keep my heart turned to You!
